			<node ID="ID_408316710" TEXT="Real-time systems are those systems in which the correctness of the system depends not only on the logical result of computation but also on the time at which the results are produced. RTOS is therefore an operating system that supports real-time applications by providing logically correct result within the deadline required." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1285201530" LINK="https://www.robomart.com/blog/real-time-operating-system-rtos/" TEXT="What is Real Time Operating System (RTOS) - Types of RTOS">
